{"tid":1722854,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"11/24 停火為區選","createTime":"2019-11-15T04:18:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T11:33:11.000Z","uid":30081,"like":17,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"746de07f6cd709420e06bbc345d6956f89ccebf4","tid":1722854,"uid":30081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:18:46.000Z","msg":"抗爭者應在本星期內24~11~2019宣佈「停火期」, 好讓區議會選舉可以順利進行。申明若再有堵路、放火&hellip;&hellip;不是由抗爭者做的，此期間民間全不進行抗爭活動，若有此等行動一概不是抗爭者所為，是有人假扮黑衣人做些誣陷抗爭者的事。<br />\n<br />\n希望「民間記者會」同文宣組盡力推廣"},{"pid":"02e755085f7d1e6c71d803192e80452452ddd77b","tid":1722854,"uid":280648,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果唔係嘅話就真係攪炒區選<br />\n雖然我知有人係想<br />\n但係重有唔少人對區選有希望<br />\n如果民主派勝出嘅話都叫比到政府睇藍絲先係少數"},{"pid":"7f690a674dd0923f3a2dc546eb04d4a95b61f35a","tid":1722854,"uid":30081,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:44:32.000Z","msg":"區選仲有9日"},{"pid":"68c650321f4daf62adb9e65fc4ef12fe6a1b9e2d","tid":1722854,"uid":44318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:44:41.000Z","msg":"DE LAG"},{"pid":"b51391f454eea306463ffb5c49ac84ea297708d4","tid":1722854,"uid":161909,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:59:04.000Z","msg":"如果制度有用 我哋仲點會需要打咁多個月"},{"pid":"eb02c0c838bcbf49eaba4d2cfe7c6247bb6f7c3f","tid":1722854,"uid":131551,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b51391f454eea306463ffb5c49ac84ea297708d4","tid":1722854,"uid":161909,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:59:04.000Z","msg":"如果制度有用 我哋仲點會需要打咁多個月"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:00:21.000Z","msg":"而家係要懲罰建制先   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n制度無用都要佢地無工開    無收入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d7f8ff54d8b02e1c921b73462be278e356a12d8","tid":1722854,"uid":306922,"like"